,(68,'texto','','{"1":"<p>The following concessions will apply during the official Group dates and are based on current block:</p>\\n\\n<p>The Company will cause the Hotel to provide one complimentary room, single or double occupancy for every 50 rooms paid nightly.&nbsp; These rooms are all-inclusive.&nbsp; (A mandatory charge of $20.00 USD per person, per night will be charged for complimentary rooms for tax and gratuities.)&nbsp; Maximum of 5 rooms.</p>\\n\\n<p>The Company will cause the Hotel to provide one Staff room at 50% of the Group rate (single or double occupancy) for every 50 rooms paid nightly up to a maximum of 6 rooms.&nbsp; Staff rates are applicable 2 nights prior, 1 night post.</p>\\n\\n<p>The Company will cause the Hotel to provide one Up-Grade to the next category level available/a one-bedroom suite [2 guests maximum] for every 50 rooms paid nightly to a maximum of 3 suites/rooms.&nbsp; Additional nights will be at the prevailing rates.</p>\\n\\n<p>The Company will cause the Hotel to provide private group functions without surcharge in meeting rooms and outdoor areas when using inclusive Hotel menus. (See exceptions under Additional Costs).</p>\\n\\n<p>The Hotel will assign a Conference Service Manager to coordinate your Group.</p>\\n\\n<p>The Company will cause the Hotel to provide a 40% discount on Green Fees at Moon Palace Golf course. Discount does not apply to twilight rate, equipment rental or pro shop. Delete if offering Resort Credit</p>\\n\\n<p>The Company will cause the Hotel to provide a 15% discount on Spa treatments (does not apply to discounted packages). Delete if offering Resort Credit.</p>\\n\\n<p>The Company will cause the Hotel to apply 3% to 5% of the total Net Room Pickup towards incidental charges billed to the master account. Net Room Pick up is defined as the total room revenue picked up less complimentary and staff rooms and after the deduction of taxes and gratuities. The credit may not be used towards reducing room revenue owed or towards any applicable liquidated damages. Credit may be used towards surcharges for private receptions in suites, tee times at Moon Palace Spa &amp; Golf Club, Spa treatments at any Palace Resort,&nbsp; Palace Productions AV &amp; d&eacute;cor services. Not applicable for any cost established in the Palace Production Technical Production Manual, nor for any cost derivative from any external supplier. No cash reimbursement if credit is not used. Unused Credit cannot be applied to future programs.</p>\\n\\n<p>The Company will cause the Hotel to offer a special amenity of $500 Resort Credit (for 3 nights) or $750 Resort Credit (for 4 nights) or $1,500 Resort Credit (for 5 to 8 nights). Credit is based on per room per stay and it is only applicable to individual guest room folio. Resort credit is non-transferable and non-cumulative. Resort Credit has no commercial value and is not subject to refund or credit. 16% Taxes and fees apply for services redeemed and will be covered by each guest. Terms and conditions at <a href=\\"http://www.leblancsparesort.com/sites/default/files/pdf/en/rcbrochure.pdf\\">http://www.leblancsparesort.com/sites/default/files/pdf/en/rcbrochure.pdf</a></p>\\n\\n<p>Each person in the group will have the opportunity to participate in the Moon Vacation Getaway program, which offers a preferential rate for a future stay.</p>\\n"}','texto@bnf_configuracion_clausula@jugomez','jugomez','2019-08-01','12:13:29',1564679609,'INSERT','')
