,(68,'texto','','{"1":"<p>Holiday Season:<br />\\n0 &ndash; 14 days prior to arrival&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3 nights Penalty<br />\\nUp to 15 days prior to arrival&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;No Penalty<br />\\nRest of the year:<br />\\n0 &ndash; 3 days prior to arrival&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1 night Penalty<br />\\nUp until 4 days prior to arrival&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; No Penalty</p>\\n\\n<ul>\\n\\t<li>Attrition will be based on the total number of room nights contracted, not on peak nights. Reduction of rooms on&nbsp;any of the Official Group Dates must apply equally for each date that is named as Official, in the previous clause of&nbsp; this contract. Failure to do so may be considered by the hotel to be a breach of contract, therefore causing the&nbsp;group to be subject to availability and re-quotation.</li>\\n\\t<li>Attrition in excess of 40% of original room block may be consider by the hotel as a total cancellation of the Group in&nbsp;the sole discretion of the hotel. For cancellation damages, please refer to cancellation penalties listed above.</li>\\n\\t<li>Attrition and no shows will be charged as single or double occupancy as contracted and calculated based on the&nbsp;examples set forth above.</li>\\n\\t<li>No-shows and early departures are NON-REFUNDABLE and will be charged for the entire stay of confirmed&nbsp;reservation.</li>\\n\\t<li>All reductions and cancellations must be made in writing prior to the cut off dates outlined. Verbal reductions and&nbsp;cancellations will not be binding.</li>\\n</ul>\\n\\n<p>Upon request, the Company will provide the Group with a copy of the Hotel&rsquo;s city ledger or daily report showing the&nbsp;information that was used by the Company to calculate the cancellation fees set forth herein. The Company agrees that,&nbsp;after it receives payment in full of all cancellation fees due pursuant to this Agreement, it will not seek additional damages&nbsp;related to the Group&rsquo;s failure to utilize its room block.</p>\\n"}','texto@bnf_configuracion_clausula@dareyes','dareyes','2019-08-01','18:03:07',1564700587,'INSERT','')
