,(68,'texto','','{"1":"<ol>\\n\\t<li>181 days or more prior to scheduled arrival no reduction damages will be assessed.</li>\\n\\t<li>Between 180-91 days, the current Group block may be reduced by 10% without damages. Any rooms released above the 10% allowed will be charged 40% of the net room revenue cancelled. .</li>\\n\\t<li>Between 90-61 days, the current Group block may be reduced by 5% without damages.&nbsp; Any rooms released above the 5% allowed will be charged 60% of the net room revenue cancelled. .</li>\\n\\t<li>Between 60-31 days, the current Group block may be reduced by 5% without damages.&nbsp; Any rooms released above the 5% allowed will be charged 75% of the net room revenue cancelled. .</li>\\n\\t<li>Between 30-8 days, the current Group block may be reduced by 3% without damages.&nbsp; Any rooms released above the 3% allowed will be charged 90% of the net room revenue cancelled. .</li>\\n\\t<li>Any reduction received 7 days or less is non-refundable.</li>\\n\\t<li>If the room block falls below 10 rooms, a cancellation of the entire group will apply.</li>\\n</ol>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Example:&nbsp;&nbsp; Contracted Room Block:&nbsp; 1,000 room nights</p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Reduction at 92 days: 300 room nights</p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Allowed 10% attrition: 100 room nights</p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Subject to damages:&nbsp; 200&nbsp;&nbsp; room nights</p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 200 room nights x [net group rate] x 40% = damages due</p>\\n","2":"<p><strong>REDUCCION DEL GRUPO</strong></p>\\n\\n<ol>\\n\\t<li>Con aviso de 181 d&iacute;as o m&aacute;s antes de la fecha de llegada del grupo, no habr&aacute; penalizaci&oacute;n.</li>\\n\\t<li>Con aviso entre 180 - 91 d&iacute;as antes de la fecha de llegada, si el grupo reduce del bloqueo actual un 10%, no habr&aacute; penalizaci&oacute;n. Si reduce m&aacute;s del 10% pagar&aacute; a El Hotel el cargo equivalente al 40% del ingreso total cancelado.</li>\\n\\t<li>Con aviso entre 90-61 d&iacute;as antes de la fecha de llegada, si el grupo reduce del bloqueo actual un 5%, no habr&aacute; penalizaci&oacute;n. Si reduce m&aacute;s del 5%, pagar&aacute; a El Hotel el cargo equivalente al 60% del ingreso total cancelado.</li>\\n\\t<li>Con aviso entre 60-31 d&iacute;as antes de la fecha de llegada, si el grupo reduce del bloqueo actual un 5%, no habr&aacute; penalizaci&oacute;n. Si reduce m&aacute;s del 5% pagar&aacute; a El Hotel el cargo equivalente al 75% del ingreso total cancelado.</li>\\n\\t<li>Con aviso entre 30-8 d&iacute;as antes de la fecha de llegada, si el grupo reduce del bloqueo actual un 3%, no habr&aacute; penalizaci&oacute;n. Si reduce m&aacute;s del 3% pagar&aacute; a El Hotel el cargo equivalente al 90% del ingreso total cancelado.</li>\\n\\t<li>Cualquier reducci&oacute;n recibida 7 d&iacute;as antes de la fecha de llegada, no ser&aacute; reembolsable.</li>\\n\\t<li>Si el bloqueo se reduce a menos de 10 habitaciones, el total del grupo quedar&aacute; cancelado.</li>\\n</ol>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Ejemplo:&nbsp;&nbsp; Bloqueo de habitaciones contratado: 800 cuartos noche</p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Reducci&oacute;n a 92 d&iacute;as: 100 cuartos noche</p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Reducci&oacute;n permitida del 10%: 80 cuartos noche</p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Penalidad: 20 cuartos noche</p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 20 cuartos noche x [tarifa grupal] x 40% = penalidad</p>\\n"}','texto@bnf_configuracion_clausula@jugomez','jugomez','2019-08-02','10:44:31',1564760671,'INSERT','')
