(68,'texto','{"1":"<ul>\\n\\t<li>King sized bed or 2 double beds. [Bed types are not guaranteed, but subject to availability.]</li>\\n\\t<li>Double Whirlpool Tub. Private bath w/ shower only. Balcony. In Room Wine. Coffee Maker. Liquor Dispenser. Mini Bar contains sodas, bottled water, juices &amp; domestic beer. CHI Bath Amenities. Bathrobes &amp; Slippers. Digital safe (laptop size). Individually-controlled A/C. Direct Dial telephone. Smart TV with Youtube, TvTuner and Weather Channel. I-dock. Hair Dryer and Straightener. Iron &amp; ironing board, garment steamer, 24-Hour room service &amp; Turndown service. Non-smoking room.</li>\\n\\t<li>All meals and drinks at the Hotel including alcoholic beverages. [No refund for unused food and beverage.]</li>\\n\\t<li>All Hotel taxes and gratuities.</li>\\n\\t<li>Wireless Internet.</li>\\n\\t<li>Most on property sports and activities. (See Appendix for details).</li>\\n\\t<li>Unlimited long distance telephone calls to the Continental USA, Canada and Mexico (please see Telephone Charges herein for details).</li>\\n\\t<li>Function Space.</li>\\n</ul>\\n","2":"<p>@ROOMSCOMP@</p>\\n"}','{"1":"<ul>\\n\\t<li>King sized bed or 2 double beds. [Bed types are not guaranteed, but subject to availability.]</li>\\n\\t<li>Double Whirlpool Tub. Private bath w/ shower only. Balcony. In Room Wine. Coffee Maker. Liquor Dispenser. Mini Bar contains sodas, bottled water, juices &amp; domestic beer. CHI Bath Amenities. Bathrobes &amp; Slippers. Digital safe (laptop size). Individually-controlled A/C. Direct Dial telephone. Smart TV with Youtube, TvTuner and Weather Channel. I-dock. Hair Dryer and Straightener. Iron &amp; ironing board, garment steamer, 24-Hour room service &amp; Turndown service. Non-smoking room.</li>\\n\\t<li>All meals and drinks at the Hotel including alcoholic beverages. [No refund for unused food and beverage.]</li>\\n\\t<li>All Hotel taxes and gratuities.</li>\\n\\t<li>Wireless Internet.</li>\\n\\t<li>Most on property sports and activities. (See Appendix for details).</li>\\n\\t<li>Unlimited long distance telephone calls to the Continental USA, Canada and Mexico (please see Telephone Charges herein for details).</li>\\n\\t<li>Function Space.</li>\\n</ul>\\n","2":"<ul>\\n\\t<li>Habitaci&oacute;n con cama King o dos camas. [el tipo de cama no est&aacute; garantizado, sujeto a disponibilidad].</li>\\n\\t<li>Balc&oacute;n con sillas. Servicio de Mayordomo. Men&uacute; de Confort (incluye almohadas especiales, sales de ba&ntilde;o, men&uacute; de aromaterapia y jabones artesanales). Servicio a la habitaci&oacute;n las 24 horas y cortes&iacute;a nocturna. Internet inal&aacute;mbrico. Botellas de vino y tequila de bienvenida. Dispensador de Licores Premium de ron, whisky y vodka. Mini Bar abastecido diariamente con refrescos, agua embotellada, jugos, cervezas nacionales e importadas. Selecci&oacute;n de aperitivos en la habitaci&oacute;n. Petit Fours nocturnos. Cafetera Lavazza&reg;. Plancha/Tabla para planchar. Caja fuerte digital (tama&ntilde;o laptop). &Aacute;rea de descanso. Aire acondicionado controlado individualmente. Tel&eacute;fono de marcaci&oacute;n directa. Smart TV con Apple TV (Aplicaciones no incluidas). Reloj despertador / Radio / iPod Dock con conexi&oacute;n Bluetooth. Exclusiva bolsa de playa (una por habitaci&oacute;n / por estancia). Paraguas. Amenidades de ba&ntilde;o marca BVLGARI&reg;. Ba&ntilde;o privado c/ ducha tipo lluvia y tina de ba&ntilde;o libre. Batas de ba&ntilde;o y pantuflas. B&aacute;scula de ba&ntilde;o. Secadora y plancha para el cabello profesional de marca CHI&reg;. Habitaci&oacute;n libre de humo.</li>\\n\\t<li>Todos los alimentos y bebidas en el hotel, incluyendo bebidas alcoh&oacute;licas (No se har&aacute;n cr&eacute;ditos ni reembolsos si el grupo o alguno de los participantes por as&iacute; convenir de sus intereses o por modificaciones al programa, falla o decide no consumir alimentos y/o bebidas).</li>\\n\\t<li>Todos los impuestos y propinas (ver ap&eacute;ndice para detalles)</li>\\n\\t<li>Internet inal&aacute;mbrico</li>\\n\\t<li>Deportes no motorizados (ver ap&eacute;ndice para detalles)</li>\\n\\t<li>Llamadas ilimitadas a tel&eacute;fonos fijos, v&aacute;lidas marcando desde su habitaci&oacute;n a toda la Rep&uacute;blica Mexicana, USA, Europa, Sudam&eacute;rica y Canad&aacute; (aplican restricciones).</li>\\n</ul>\\n"}','4','marrosas','2019-09-02','11:37:03',1567442223,'UPDATE','')
