(68,'texto','{"1":"<ul>\\n\\t<li>@PRUEBA_NUMERO_CR_3__ROOMS@The following concessions will apply during the official Group dates and are based on current block:</li>\\n</ul>\\n\\n<p>-The Company will cause the Hotel to provide one complimentary room, single or double occupancy for every @ROOMSCOMP@ rooms paid nightly.&nbsp; These rooms are all-inclusive.&nbsp; (A mandatory charge of @TIPS@ USD per person, per night will be charged for complimentary rooms for tax and gratuities.)&nbsp; Maximum of @AMOUNT_COMPLEMENTARY@ rooms.</p>\\n\\n<p>-The Company will cause the Hotel to provide one Staff room at 50% of the Group rate (single or double occupancy) for every @ROOMSCOMP@ rooms paid nightly up to a maximum of @AMOUNT_COMPLEMENTARY@ rooms.&nbsp; Staff rates are applicable 2 nights prior, 1 night post.</p>\\n\\n<p>-The Company will cause the Hotel to provide one Up-Grade to the next category level available/a one-bedroom suite [2 guests maximum] for every @ROOMSCOMP@ rooms paid nightly to a maximum of @AMOUNT_COMPLEMENTARY@ suites/rooms.&nbsp; Additional nights will be at the prevailing rates.</p>\\n\\n<p>-The Company will cause the Hotel to provide private group functions without surcharge in meeting rooms and outdoor areas when using inclusive Hotel menus. (See exceptions under Additional Costs).</p>\\n\\n<p>-The Hotel will assign a Conference Service Manager to coordinate your Group.</p>\\n\\n<p>-The Company will cause the Hotel to provide a @GREENFEES@% discount on Green Fees at Moon Palace Golf course. Discount does not apply to twilight rate, equipment rental or pro shop. Delete if offering Resort Credit</p>\\n\\n<p>-The Company will cause the Hotel to provide a @SPAPORCENT@% discount on Spa treatments (does not apply to discounted packages). Delete if offering Resort Credit.</p>\\n\\n<p>-The Company will cause the Hotel to apply 3% to 5% of the total Net Room Pickup towards incidental charges billed to the master account. Net Room Pick up is defined as the total room revenue picked up less complimentary and staff rooms and after the deduction of taxes and gratuities. The credit may not be used towards reducing room revenue owed or towards any applicable liquidated damages. Credit may be used towards surcharges for private receptions in suites, tee times at Moon Palace Spa &amp; Golf Club, Spa treatments at any Palace Resort,&nbsp; Palace Productions AV &amp; d&eacute;cor services. Not applicable for any cost established in the Palace Production Technical Production Manual, nor for any cost derivative from any external supplier. No cash reimbursement if credit is not used. Unused Credit cannot be applied to future programs.</p>\\n\\n<p>-The Company will cause the Hotel to offer a special amenity of @RESORT_CREDIT@&nbsp;Resort Credit (for 3 nights) or $@RESORT_CREDIT@(750) Resort Credit (for 4 nights) or $@RESORT_CREDIT@(1,500) Resort Credit (for 5 to 8 nights). Credit is based on per room per stay and it is only applicable to individual guest room folio. Resort credit is non-transferable and non-cumulative. Resort Credit has no commercial value and is not subject to refund or credit. 16% Taxes and fees apply for services redeemed and will be covered by each guest. Terms and conditions at <a href=\\"http://www.leblancsparesort.com/sites/default/files/pdf/en/rcbrochure.pdf\\">http://www.leblancsparesort.com/sites/default/files/pdf/en/rcbrochure.pdf</a></p>\\n\\n<p>-Each person in the group will have the opportunity to participate in the Moon Vacation Getaway program, which offers a preferential rate for a future stay.</p>\\n","2":"<ol>\\n\\t<li>C&oacute;ctel de Bienvenida con Barra Libre Internacional acompa&ntilde;ada de Canap&eacute;s.</li>\\n\\t<li>Cena de Bienvenida tipo Bufete en Terraza (No incluye M&uacute;sica, fiestas tema o escenograf&iacute;as).</li>\\n\\t<li>Cena de Clausura en sal&oacute;n con men&uacute; de 03 tiempos. A escoger de los men&uacute;s preestablecidos por EL HOTEL. (No incluye M&uacute;sica, estrado, pista de baile o montajes especiales)</li>\\n\\t<li>Incluye 5 horas de servicio de meseros en eventos privados.</li>\\n\\t<li>&Aacute;rea de registro especial, sujeta a disponibilidad al momento de la firma de contrato y&nbsp; de acuerdo al n&uacute;mero y hora de llegada de los participantes.</li>\\n\\t<li>Barra de Bebidas y canap&eacute;s durante el registro.</li>\\n\\t<li>Salones incluidos de acuerdo al n&uacute;mero de participantes hospedados en el hotel.</li>\\n\\t<li>Coffee Break cont&iacute;nuo durante todas sus sesiones (caf&eacute;, agua, refrescos, pan dulce, pastas, crudittes y/o snacks).</li>\\n\\t<li>EL HOTEL le asignar&aacute; un Gerente de Grupos exclusivo para el evento.</li>\\n\\t<li>Eventos privados en sal&oacute;n y en &aacute;reas exteriores autorizadas.</li>\\n\\t<li>Un cuarto noche en ocupaci&oacute;n sencilla o doble al 50% de descuento sobre la tarifa grupal por cada @ROOMSCOMP@ habitaciones pagadas por noche, para el staff de LA EMPRESA/AGENCIA/EL CLIENTE, v&aacute;lido durante las fechas grupales (00 al 00 mes del 2000), Tarifas de staff son aplicables 2 noches antes y 1 noche despu&eacute;s de las fechas grupales. Noches adicionales, aplicar&aacute;n las tarifas grupales. M&aacute;ximo @AMOUNT_COMPLEMENTARY@habitaciones</li>\\n\\t<li>Un cuarto noche sencillo o doble en cortes&iacute;a por cada @ROOMSCOMP@ habitaciones pagadas por noche, v&aacute;lidas durante las fechas grupales, noches antes y/o despu&eacute;s&nbsp; aplica las tarifas grupales. Estas habitaciones son en plan Todo Incluido. (Se cobrar&aacute;n $@TIPS@USD por persona, por noche por concepto de impuestos y propinas.) M&aacute;ximo @AMOUNT_COMPLEMENTARY@ habitaciones.</li>\\n\\t<li>Un up-grade de habitaci&oacute;n a suite de una recamara por cada @ROOMSCOMP@ Habitaciones pagadas por noche, v&aacute;lidas durante las fechas grupales (00 al 00 de mes del 2018), noches antes y/o despu&eacute;s&nbsp; aplica las tarifas grupales. Sujeto a disponibilidad a la firma del contrato y primer pago. M&aacute;ximo @AMOUNT_COMPLEMENTARY@ habitaciones.</li>\\n\\t<li>Botella de vino de bienvenida para las habitaciones del grupo la primera noche de estancia.</li>\\n\\t<li>Acceso a todos los hoteles de Palace Resorts en plan todo incluido (Excepto Hotel Le blanc y The Grand at Moon Palace).</li>\\n\\t<li>&ldquo;EL HOTEL&rdquo; otorgar&aacute; un descuento del @GREENFEES@% sobre las rondas de Golf en los campos de Golf en Moon Palace Canc&uacute;n y Canc&uacute;n Riviera. El descuento no aplica a&nbsp;renta de equipo, zapatos y tienda.&nbsp;</li>\\n\\t<li>&ldquo;EL HOTEL&rdquo; otorgar&aacute; un descuento del @SPAPORCENT@% en tratamientos de Spa (no aplica en paquetes en promoci&oacute;n)</li>\\n\\t<li>EL HOTEL otorgar&aacute; un bono del 5 % del monto total del evento generado por rentas de habitaci&oacute;n, que podr&aacute; ser utilizado para pago de extras del grupo, como Spa, Golf, exclusivo para proveedores in-house autorizados. El monto se calcula despu&eacute;s de haber deducido $20.00 USD por persona, por noche, por concepto de propinas e impuestos de las tarifas grupales. Este monto no aplica para pago de habitaciones, no se dar&aacute;n cr&eacute;ditos ni reembolsos en efectivo por servicios no utilizados y no es acumulable con otros grupos.</li>\\n</ol>\\n"}','{"1":"<ul>\\n\\t<li>The Company will cause the Hotel to provide one complimentary room, single or double occupancy for every @PRODUCTION_PEAK_NIGHTS@ rooms paid nightly. These rooms are all-inclusive. (A mandatory charge of $20.00 USD per person, per night will be charged for complimentary rooms for tax and gratuities.) Maximum of @MAX_DE_COMPS@ rooms.</li>\\n</ul>\\n","2":"<ol>\\n\\t<li>C&oacute;ctel de Bienvenida con Barra Libre Internacional acompa&ntilde;ada de Canap&eacute;s.</li>\\n\\t<li>Cena de Bienvenida tipo Bufete en Terraza (No incluye M&uacute;sica, fiestas tema o escenograf&iacute;as).</li>\\n\\t<li>Cena de Clausura en sal&oacute;n con men&uacute; de 03 tiempos. A escoger